FY 2026 Plans:
In FY2026, the program office is initiating a rapid prototyping contract to build test articles for an affordable threat
emitter design concept that has the potential to fulfill a set of current shortfalls in live-emitter training needs
for the F-35 aircraft and other aircraft platforms at regional training ranges. Success of this effort will inform
divestment decisions for aging legacy range emitters that are well beyond service life and facing significant
sustainment obsolescence challenges and rising repair costs.
