 FINANCIAL PERFORMANCE:GPS IIIF is evaluated against traditional Research and Development (R&D) program expenditure benchmarks. Unlike many traditional R&D
 programs, however, the GPS IIIF Development contract is a FPIF contract with progress payments. 10 percent of incurred costs are withheld until the end of the contract, when
 they are liquidated. Mandatory funding obligations and progress payment withholds will cause the program to lag traditional expenditure benchmarks, painting an inaccurate
 portrait of overall program execution health.




