 Acquisition strategies will vary depending on what is appropriate to the project to be executed but will include support from the following: Industry, University Affiliated
 Research Center(s) (UARC), Other Transaction Authorities (OTA), Federally Funded Research & Development Centers (FFRDC), Industry Consortia, and other
 sources. Initial plans leverage existing efforts and their existing contract mechanism continuing and/or expanding the scope of work to meet Advanced EW Capability
 needs. Once initial infrastructure and capabilities are in place, long term contracts will be required to maintain throughput.

