Remarks
 DAF Electromagnetic Battle Management (EMBM) System-of-Systems Integration will pull all contributing systems and applications into a cohesive and effective single user
 interface as well as work on porting the USAF data to the EMBM-J platform.

DAF EMBM Platform Integration will explore how to transfer raw spectrum data between aircraft and ground stations and return EMBM operational data from ground station to
aircraft

The Training Module will be developed alongside the actual EMBM system so when it is fielded, those presented with the system will know how to utilize it in pursuit of
Electromagnetic Spectrum Operation (EMSO) execution.

IT Infrastructure will set the standards and requirements required for the EMBM system to connect and interact with the future DAF Battle Network.

PMA will allow for the Program Office to conduct the ongoing Early Operational Concept developmental efforts.

