                                                                                                                        FY 2024    FY 2025      Base        OOC        Total
1) Semi-annual delivery/test cycle for Terminal Defense hard-kill and soft-kill capability (in a combination of Gray
Flag events), 2) Quarterly delivery/test cycle for Long Range Fire capabilities (in a combination of Gray Flag and
other events).
