A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
Automated Test and ReTest (ATRT) Enterprise Rapid Capability develops, integrates, and deploys novel capabilities aggregated from mature technologies in support of
Distributed Maritime Operations. These capabilities are enabled through the use of virtualized systems of systems, automated test and analysis, automated certification,
rapid interface development, and field with and data collection and edge analytics.. These technologies are at the heart of the Navy's rapid capability approach, which
combines digital engineering tools with evolutionary approaches to requirements generation, operational testing, and deployment. This process will meet Fleet demands
for near-term capability in a predictable and repeatable fashion.

