Title: M Code                                                                                                                                 0.000       0.000          3.018
Description: The current aircraft Embedded GPS/INS (EGI) system suffers from Diminishing Manufacturing Sources (DMS)
shortfalls. New security requirements and mandated M-code Enhancement of Positioning, Navigation, and Timing Capacity (PNT)
hardware support drive the need for a new EGI solution to support modern resilient weaponry and mission systems. Selected
solution Resilient-EGI, development managed by AFLCMC/WNY. F-16 will then integrate R-EGI onto the F-16 platform.

FY 2026 Plans:
N/A
FY 2027 Plans:
